      • isRowAccepted

        boolean isRowAccepted(TableModel model,
                    int row)
        Check if the given row is accepted for the filter. If this method returns true when the row will be available.
        Parameters:
        model - The underlying table model
        row - the row to check.
        Returns:
        true if the row should be available, false if not.
